  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK617">
<l>maṭiyuḷāṇ māmukaṭi yeṉpamaṭiyilāṉ </l>
<l> ṟāḷuḷā ṭāmaraiyi ṉāḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They say that the black Mudevi (the goddess of adversity) dwells with laziness, and the Latchmi (the goddess of prosperity) dwells with the labour of the industrious.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
